apsedTime</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nt\">this-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">stop</span> <span class=\"nt\">-</span> <span class=\"nt\">this-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">start</span><span class=\"o\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">//</span> <span class=\"nt\">If</span> <span class=\"nt\">we</span><span class=\"err\">&#39;</span><span class=\"nt\">re</span> <span class=\"nt\">counting</span> <span class=\"nt\">down</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">return</span> <span class=\"nt\">the</span> <span class=\"nt\">countdown</span> <span class=\"nt\">time</span> <span class=\"nt\">minus</span> <span class=\"nt\">the</span> <span class=\"nt\">total</span>\n<span class=\"o\">//</span> <span class=\"nt\">elapsed</span> <span class=\"nt\">time</span><span class=\"o\">.</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">if</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">this-</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"nt\">countdown</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"err\">elapsedTime</span> <span class=\"err\">=</span> <span class=\"err\">this-&gt;maxTime</span> <span class=\"err\">-</span> <span class=\"err\">elapsedTime</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"err\">//</span> <span class=\"err\">If</span> <span class=\"err\">out</span> <span class=\"err\">of</span> <span class=\"err\">time</span>\n  <span class=\"err\">if</span> <span class=\"err\">(elapsedTime</span> <span class=\"err\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"err\">0)</span>\n    <span class=\"err\">elapsedTime</span> <span class=\"err\">=</span> <span class=\"err\">Time(0)</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">return</span> <span class=\"nt\">elapsedTime</span><span class=\"o\">;</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-05-20T01:16:46.019596+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2